data.description: One Level Living.  Private and Convenient.  This Home is like New and on a permanent foundation. The open floor plan offers a large family area.  The Kitchen/dining area offers a great space for the family meals. The primary bedroom is spacious along with the primary bath. The home offers 2 more bedrooms and a bath.  Outside, there is a RV hookup area.  The home sits well back from the road for privacy. The 2.5 acres is covered with wildlife yet you are 5 minutes to shopping and Bristol Speedway. See it today.  Please allow one hour notice for showings.  (pets)
